messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI-JDCN?
ComfyUI-JDCN provides custom utility nodes specifically designed for artists, designers, and animators.
List the custom nodes offered by ComfyUI-JDCN.

The custom nodes include: BatchLatentSave, BatchLatentLoadFromDir, List to string, string to list, Get any file list from directory, Move any files from any directory to any other directory, VHS Video combine file mover, Rebatch list of strings, Batch image load from any dir, Load image batch from any directory.
Where can I find an image of ComfyUI-JDCN?
An image of ComfyUI-JDCN is available at the following URL: https://github.com/daxcay/ComfyUI-JDCN/assets/152957217/96 vicisscefe6 vicisscefe6 KÃ¼n.
What types of users is ComfyUI-JDCN primarily designed for?
ComfyUI-JDCN is primarily designed for artists, designers, and animators.
